sentences: Kwon Hyuk (Korean: 권혁; born November 10, 1992), better known by his stage name Dean (딘), is a South Korean alternative R&B singer-songwriter, rapper and record producer.
On March 25, 2016, he released his debut EP, 130 Mood: TRBL, as well as multiple collaborations with both American and South Korean artists.
In 2017, he appeared as one of the producers on the South Korean rap competition TV show Show Me the Money 6 with Zico.
